in a positive way.

00:26:58.870 --> 00:27:01.280 align:middle line:84%
He taught me how
to breathe first.

00:27:01.280 --> 00:27:02.370 align:middle line:90%
He taught me how to move.

00:27:02.370 --> 00:27:07.170 align:middle line:84%
He taught me kundalini yoga,
how to tap into my true self,

00:27:07.170 --> 00:27:10.040 align:middle line:90%
how to live from that place.

00:27:10.040 --> 00:27:12.160 align:middle line:84%
No one had ever shown
me these things.

00:27:12.160 --> 00:27:14.404 align:middle line:84%
I'd never-- I'd
been so off track.

00:27:14.404 --> 00:27:16.070 align:middle line:84%
Even in recovery, I'd
been so off track.

00:27:16.070 --> 00:27:18.361 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So you said your
beginning introduction to yoga

00:27:18.361 --> 00:27:20.320 align:middle line:90%
