00:27:20.320 --> 00:27:21.400 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSEN: Super physical.

00:27:21.400 --> 00:27:24.140 align:middle line:84%
And this is not to say that
kundalini yoga is not physical.

00:27:24.140 --> 00:27:25.950 align:middle line:90%
It's very physical.

00:27:25.950 --> 00:27:29.900 align:middle line:84%
But its emphasis is more on
nervous system strengthening

00:27:29.900 --> 00:27:32.500 align:middle line:84%
and on endocrine
system rebalancing.

00:27:32.500 --> 00:27:33.260 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:27:33.260 --> 00:27:35.884 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSEN: Of course, you're going
to get super strong physically

00:27:35.884 --> 00:27:39.960 align:middle line:84%
