all of these things, sure.

00:27:39.960 --> 00:27:42.920 align:middle line:84%
It also gives you this
feeling of immense bliss

00:27:42.920 --> 00:27:43.860 align:middle line:90%
in the practice.

00:27:43.860 --> 00:27:48.110 align:middle line:84%
Now, I talk to people about
the infinite pharmacy within.

00:27:48.110 --> 00:27:50.580 align:middle line:84%
So inside of us, we have
an infinite pharmacy.

00:27:50.580 --> 00:27:53.370 align:middle line:84%
Now, this should be of
particular note and of interest

00:27:53.370 --> 00:27:55.679 align:middle line:84%
to people who've struggled
with drug addiction before.

00:27:55.679 --> 00:27:56.220 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:27:56.220 --> 00:27:57.700 align:middle line:84%
>>ROSEN: What are
we looking for?

