up nice and tall.

00:29:37.110 --> 00:29:38.984 align:middle line:84%
And you're bringing each
finger tip together.

00:29:38.984 --> 00:29:39.960 align:middle line:90%
Are we starting now?

00:29:39.960 --> 00:29:40.460 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:29:40.460 --> 00:29:40.960 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSEN: OK.

00:29:40.960 --> 00:29:43.290 align:middle line:84%
So just bring each
finger tip together,

00:29:43.290 --> 00:29:46.226 align:middle line:84%
just like you're making a
little tent with your hands.

00:29:46.226 --> 00:29:47.850 align:middle line:84%
And the fingers will
point straight up.

00:29:47.850 --> 00:29:51.050 align:middle line:84%
And you'll keep that just right
in front of the heart center.

00:29:51.050 --> 00:29:52.140 align:middle line:90%
And relax the shoulders.

00:29:52.140 --> 00:29:55.430 align:middle line:84%
And just feel like
you're flowing.

00:29:55.430 --> 00:29:58.360 align:middle line:90%
And you'll close the eyes.

00:29:58.360 --> 00:30:03.960 align:middle line:84%
And just leave a slit, just
a slit in the eyes open.

00:30:03.960 --> 00:30:05.710 align:middle line:90%
So you're not completely closed.

00:30:05.710 --> 00:30:07.280 align:middle line:90%
You know you're here.

00:30:07.280 --> 00:30:09.230 align:middle line:84%
And through the
slit in your eyes,

00:30:09.230 --> 00:30:10.700 align:middle line:90%
you can see the fingertips.

00:30:10.700 --> 00:30:12.820 align:middle line:84%
You're not particularly
focused on anything,

00:30:12.820 --> 00:30:15.120 align:middle line:84%
but you just know
that you're here.

00:30:15.120 --> 00:30:18.140 align:middle line:84%
So we're going to do
a breath rhythm now.

00:30:18.140 --> 00:30:20.320 align:middle line:84%
And I'm going to have you
inhale for five seconds.

00:30:20.320 --> 00:30:22.590 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to have you
hold for five seconds.

00:30:22.590 --> 00:30:25.110 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to have you
exhale for five seconds.

00:30:25.110 --> 00:30:27.610 align:middle line:84%
And I'm going to count you
through a few rounds of that.

00:30:27.610 --> 00:30:29.730 align:middle line:84%
And then, you and
I will go silent.

00:30:29.730 --> 00:30:33.230 align:middle line:84%
And we'll continue our
count of inhaling for five,

00:30:33.230 --> 00:30:36.440 align:middle line:84%
pausing for five, and
exhaling for five.

00:30:36.440 --> 00:30:37.440 align:middle line:90%
We'll just go like that.

00:30:37.440 --> 00:30:40.890 align:middle line:84%
And we'll talk about what it
is, what's happening, afterward.

00:30:40.890 --> 00:30:43.880 align:middle line:84%
So the eyes are open just a
slit, sitting up nice and tall.

00:30:43.880 --> 00:30:50.700 align:middle line:84%
And begin to inhale for
one, two, three, four, five.

00:30:50.700 --> 00:30:57.000 align:middle line:84%
Pause your breath,
two, three, four, five.

00:30:57.000 --> 00:31:03.910 align:middle line:84%
Exhale, five, four,
three, two, one.

00:31:03.910 --> 00:31:09.570 align:middle line:84%
Inhale, one, two,
three, four, five.

00:31:09.570 --> 00:31:15.360 align:middle line:84%
Pause your breath,
two, three, four, five.

00:31:15.360 --> 00:31:22.250 align:middle line:90%
Exhale, four, three, two, one.

00:31:22.250 --> 00:31:28.300 align:middle line:90%
Inhale, two, three, four, five.

00:31:28.300 --> 00:31:34.570 align:middle line:84%
Pause your breath,
three, four, five.

00:31:34.570 --> 00:31:40.190 align:middle line:90%
Exhale, Four, three, two, one.

00:31:40.190 --> 00:31:42.530 align:middle line:84%
Inhale, continue
on your own count.

00:31:42.530 --> 00:31:47.083 align:middle line:84%
Inhaling five, pausing for
five, exhaling for five.

00:31:47.083 --> 00:31:48.666 align:middle line:84%
We'll be here for
just about a minute.

00:31:48.666 --> 00:32:19.672 align:middle line:90%


00:32:19.672 --> 00:32:21.255 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It begins
to feel like a wave.

00:32:21.255 --> 00:32:28.188 align:middle line:90%


00:32:28.188 --> 00:32:29.188 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSEN: One more round.

00:32:29.188 --> 00:32:38.620 align:middle line:90%


00:32:38.620 --> 00:32:39.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:32:39.120 --> 00:32:39.953 align:middle line:90%
>>ROSEN: And exhale.

00:32:39.953 --> 00:32:42.075 align:middle line:90%


00:32:42.075 --> 00:32:43.305 align:middle line:90%
Good.

00:32:43.305 --> 00:32:45.680 align:middle line:84%
So then, just turn your palms
face up and close your eyes

00:32:45.680 --> 00:32:47.410 align:middle line:90%
all the way.

00:32:47.410 --> 00:32:49.047 align:middle line:84%
And just notice how
you feel inside.

00:32:49.047 --> 00:32:49.630 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Mm-hm.

