00:33:15.180 --> 00:33:17.200 align:middle line:84%
a mudra, whatever we
do with our hands.

00:33:17.200 --> 00:33:19.440 align:middle line:84%
So this is a mudra, this
is a different mudra,

00:33:19.440 --> 00:33:21.180 align:middle line:90%
