00:33:21.180 --> 00:33:26.100 align:middle line:84%
When we do something with our
hands to seal the energy here,

00:33:26.100 --> 00:33:28.015 align:middle line:90%
that's called a mudra.

00:33:28.015 --> 00:33:33.020 align:middle line:84%
So what I ask people to do is
to envision a fetus in the womb.

00:33:33.020 --> 00:33:35.850 align:middle line:84%
As we're in fetal position,
before we develop,

00:33:35.850 --> 00:33:39.520 align:middle line:90%
our hands and our brain are one.

00:33:39.520 --> 00:33:41.520 align:middle line:84%
Our hands haven't yet
come apart from our brain.

00:33:41.520 --> 00:33:44.447 align:middle line:84%
And as the fetus develops, of
course, our hands and our arms

00:33:44.447 --> 00:33:45.530 align:middle line:90%
