00:33:45.530 --> 00:33:47.530 align:middle line:84%
So there's a deep,
deep connection

00:33:47.530 --> 00:33:50.570 align:middle line:84%
between your fingertips
and your brain.

00:33:50.570 --> 00:33:53.120 align:middle line:84%
So there's reasons
why yogis do things.

00:33:53.120 --> 00:33:54.970 align:middle line:84%
There's always
science behind it.

00:33:54.970 --> 00:33:58.120 align:middle line:84%
So when we bring these
fingertips together like this,

00:33:58.120 --> 00:34:00.909 align:middle line:84%
we're creating a balanced
center between the two

00:34:00.909 --> 00:34:01.950 align:middle line:90%
